name: Artcafe
location_string: El Nido, Palawan Island, Palawan Province, Mimaropa
description: Artcafe is a popular restaurant, opens the doors early morning for breakfast with the best homemade bread, Yogurt, Swiss Muesli etc and right at the gate to the island hopping tours. It's a good hangout anytime of the day to have a bite or a coffee, a fruit shake, a cocktail or a sumptious meal, book a tour or a ticket. Artcafe grows its own organic vegetable and prides itself to be an ecofriendly and sustainable business. At night the place lights up, live music begins and you can enjoy delicious international specialities and a great variation of salads that are grown on their own organic farm or enjoy a good glass of wine and meet people at the Bar. Wifi - Books - Foreign exchange - Travel & Tour booking desk - Rentals of Kayaks, Paddle boards and Snorkel gear - General Sales Agent for El Nido Flights (Air Swift) - Airline ticketing - Van and Boat tickets - Up-to-date Information.

We used authentic ingredients directly imported from India. We offer Seven Appetizers and Sixteen Vegan Dishes and Vegetarian. We offer Ten Paneer dishes (cottage Cheese), Sixteen Chicken Dishes, Eight Mutton (Lamb), Four Fish & Prawn, and two egg curry. We offer Fourteen Basmati Rice dishes such as Pulao, Vegetarian Biryani, Chicken Biryani, and Mutton Biryani. Plenty of choice for Chapatti, Naan and Paratha. Homemade Yogurt drink, Raita, Juice, soft drink, Beer and Chai Tea ( Indian Masala Tea). The total seating capacity is 132 people. We accept a reservation, take away and dine in.

We serve a variety of ingredient-driven dishes, with something for everybody to enjoy (children and those with dietary restrictions included). Ingredients are fresh, locally sourced and of the highest quality. Our internationally trained chef-owners expertly prepare each dish, together with their team, in the open kitchen. Home made breads are baked fresh and enhance each dish they are served with. Desserts are so divine and should not be missed. We host our guests in the modern, clean, island-inspired dining room. Island-inspired cocktails, juices and shakes use house made mixers and fresh fruits. Our staff is knowledgeable and friendly and is ready to serve customers with a warm smile.

description: Enjoy the day at on one of the best beaches in El Nido, Seven Commando Beach. The pick up place is in front of Last Frontier Resort. Alternatively, you can reach us with a Kayak in 45min from El Nido or Corong Corong. The shuttle boat is included with the following two options: “SUNSET DINNER” Includes a 3-course dinner P 2’900/pers. “ROMANTIC DINNER” Ideal for a proposal, celebrating an anniversary Includes a 3-course dinner, bottle of wine P 8900 for 2 pers. (Optional roses, champagne, birthday cake) The “Romantic Dinner” option requires at least 50% down payment and needs to be reserved ahead We normally pick up the guest around 6pm, return around 9pm Please note, we don’t have a credit card machine and accept besides of Pesos, USD and Euro. We also accept Paypal, 4,5% fees applies.
